2:T90d,[{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Place","name":"East Village","description":"The East Village carries its punk-rock DNA into the present with remarkable grace — the neighborhood that birthed CBGB and the New York hardcore scene now hosts Michelin-starred restaurants, but it ha","url":"https://withpush.co/neighborhoods/east-village","geo":{"@type":"GeoCoordinates","latitude":40.7265,"longitude":-73.9815},"address":{"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"East Village","addressRegion":"NY","addressCountry":"US"},"containedInPlace":{"@type":"City","name":"New York City"}},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"How does Push work in East Village?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Push connects local creators with merchants in East Village, Manhattan. Creators visit participating businesses, scan a QR code to verify their visit, then publish content. Merchants pay only for verified foot traffic — no guessing required."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How many campaigns are active in East Village right now?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"East Village currently has 24 active creator campaigns across 31 merchants, with 112 creators operating in this neighborhood."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What is the average campaign payout in East Village?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The average campaign payout in East Village is $38 per verified visit. Total verified visits in this neighborhood have reached 3,287."}}]},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"ItemList","name":"Featured Merchants in East Village","numberOfItems":3,"itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"item":{"@type":"LocalBusiness","name":"Momofuku Noodle Bar","address":"171 1st Ave, New York, NY 10003","description":"Food & Drink business in East Village with 2 active Push campaigns."}},{"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"item":{"@type":"LocalBusiness","name":"Death & Co","address":"433 E 6th St, New York, NY 10009","description":"Nightlife business in East Village with 1 active Push campaign."}},{"@type":"ListItem","position":3,"item":{"@type":"LocalBusiness","name":"Ippudo NY","address":"65 4th Ave, New York, NY 10003","description":"Food & Drink business in East Village with 3 active Push campaigns."}}]}]4:T468,The East Village carries its punk-rock DNA into the present with remarkable grace — the neighborhood that birthed CBGB and the New York hardcore scene now hosts Michelin-starred restaurants, but it hasn't sanitized itself into a caricature. Avenue A through C still has enough rough edges to feel honest. St. Marks Place is a permanent street fair of tattoo parlors, vintage shops, Japanese curry restaurants, and bars that have survived decades of rent pressure. Push campaigns in the East Village tend toward the experiential: ramen restaurants launching after-midnight menus, record shops running special listening events, underground bars hosting tasting nights. The creator community here is one of the most engaged on the platform — creators who live in or near the East Village understand the neighborhood's ethos and produce content that resonates authentically with its regulars. Top performing campaign categories: Food & Drink (Japanese/Korean/Mexican dominant), Nightlife, Record/Music, Tattoo & Body Art. Verified visit volumes peak Thursday through Saturday, with Sunday brunch as a consistent secondary surge.0:{"rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","main",null,{"className":"nh-page","children":[["$","section",null,{"className":"nhd-hero","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container nhd-hero-inner","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"nhd-breadcrumb","aria-label":"Breadcrumb","children":[["$","$L3",null,{"href":"/","children":"Push"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"nhd-breadcrumb-sep","children":"/"}],["$","$L3",null,{"href":"/neighborhoods","ch